com.salimov.yurii.service.data.interfaces

Interface DataService<T extends Model,E extends java.lang.Number>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Entity type, extends Model.
    E - Entity id type, extends Number.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ArticleService, CategoryService, CompanyService, ContentService<T,E>, MediaService<T,E>, MessageService, PhotoService, ResponseService, SectionService, UserService, VideoService
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArticleServiceImpl, CategoryServiceImpl, CompanyServiceImpl, ContentServiceImpl, DataServiceImpl, MediaServiceImpl, MessageServiceImpl, PhotoServiceImpl, ResponseServiceImpl, SectionServiceImpl, UserServiceImpl, VideoServiceImpl

    public interface DataService<T extends Model,E extends java.lang.Number>
    The interface of the service layer, describes a set of methods for working with objects of Model class or subclasses.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Yurii Salimov (yurii.alex.salimov@gmail.com)
    See Also:
    Model, ArticleService, CategoryService, ContentService, MediaService, PhotoService, ResponseService, SectionService, UserService, VideoService
